    <item>
      <title>游龙门奉先寺</title>
      <link>https://ishawnma.github.io/blog/post/poem/dufu/visiting-fengxian-temple-at-longmen/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Mar 2021 10:48:47 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://ishawnma.github.io/blog/post/poem/dufu/visiting-fengxian-temple-at-longmen/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;游龙门奉先寺&#34;&gt;游龙门奉先寺&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;已从招提游，更宿招提境。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;阴壑生虚籁，月林散清影。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;天阙象纬逼，云卧衣裳冷。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;欲觉闻晨钟，令人发深省。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
